# file slackmatic/README.slackmatic
# wcm, 2005.11.16 - 2007.04.12
# ===
This is slackmatic, a package build system for Slackware.

REQUIRES:

  * rc_static
      the plan 9 shell, installed in /bin/rc

  * httpup
      for using/synchronizing with remote repositories

  * fakeroot
      for building package as non-root user

NOTES

1.  Executables are installed in /usr/bin.

2.  Configuration files installed in /etc/slackmatic.

### EOF
